---
const pilares = [
  {
    numero: '01',
    tag: 'atendimento',
    titulo: 'Atendimento centralizado',
    texto:
      'Todas as conversas do WhatsApp num inbox só, com histórico completo. Nada se perde, nenhum cliente fica sem resposta.',
    icone:
      'M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 20l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z',
  },
  {
    numero: '02',
    tag: 'agenda',
    titulo: 'Agenda organizada',
    texto:
      'Horários, serviços e equipe num painel simples — com lembretes automáticos que confirmam presença e reduzem falta.',
    icone:
      'M8 2v4M16 2v4M3 10h18M5 4h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z',
  },
  {
    numero: '03',
    tag: 'controle',
    titulo: 'IA com controle humano',
    texto:
      'A Maya trabalha; você comanda. Ligue e desligue a IA por conversa, acompanhe cada mensagem e assuma quando quiser.',
    icone:
      'M12 2a7 7 0 0 1 7 7v3.5a7 7 0 0 1-14 0V9a7 7 0 0 1 7-7zM9 10h.01M15 10h.01M12 22v-3',
  },
];
---

<section class="border-y border-line bg-bg-warm py-16 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 md:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-brand uppercase" data-reveal>
          Por que Marca AI
        </p>
        <h2 class="max-w-xl text-3xl md:text-5xl" data-reveal>
          Três promessas. <span class="text-brand">Um sistema só.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-sm text-muted" data-reveal>
        Não é mais um inbox de WhatsApp: é o sistema operacional do seu atendimento.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-line md:mt-16">
      {
        pilares.map((p, i) => (
          <article
            class="group relative grid items-start gap-x-6 gap-y-3 border-b border-line py-8 transition-colors duration-500 [grid-template-columns:auto_1fr] hover:bg-bg md:grid-cols-[110px_64px_1fr_auto] md:items-center md:gap-x-12 md:py-12"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay={i * 0.08}
          >
            <span
              class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-line transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:text-brand md:text-7xl"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              {p.numero}
            </span>
            <span class="mt-2 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-soft text-brand transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:bg-brand group-hover:text-white md:mt-0">
              <svg
                class="h-7 w-7"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.8"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                aria-hidden="true"
              >
                <path d={p.icone} />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">{p.titulo}</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-muted">{p.texto}</p>
            </div>
            <span class="hidden rounded-full border border-line px-4 py-1.5 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-muted uppercase transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:border-brand group-hover:text-brand md:inline-flex">
              {p.tag}
            </span>
            <span
              class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-1 origin-top scale-y-0 bg-brand transition-transform duration-500 [transition-timing-function:var(--ease-out-expo)] group-hover:scale-y-100"
              aria-hidden="true"
            />
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
